#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.41:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga"
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Vidhāsutta"
msgstr "41. Discriminations"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.41:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā tisso vidhā "
"pajahiṃsu, sabbe te sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, all the ascetics and brahmins in the past who have given up the "
"three discriminations have done so by developing and cultivating the seven "
"awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā tisso vidhā "
"pajahissanti, sabbe te sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""
"All the ascetics and brahmins in the future who will give up the three "
"discriminations will do so by developing and cultivating the seven awakening "
"factors."

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā tisso vidhā pajahanti, "
"sabbe te sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""
"All the ascetics and brahmins in the present who are giving up the three "
"discriminations do so by developing and cultivating the seven awakening "
"factors."

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.5"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.6"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa."
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.7"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā tisso vidhā "
"pajahiṃsu … pe …"
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the past …"

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.8"
msgid "pajahissanti … pe …"
msgstr "future …"

msgctxt "sn46.41:1.9"
msgid ""
"pajahanti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā "
"bahulīkatattā”ti."
msgstr ""
"and present who give up the three discriminations do so by developing and "
"cultivating the seven awakening factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.41:1.10"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
